cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper deals with deep learning architecture for probabilistic future prediction from video, which involves scene understanding and control of an autonomous vehicle. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also deals with controlling an autonomous vehicle, which falls under robotics (cs.RO). The paper uses a conditional variational approach, which is a machine learning technique, and hence it could also belong to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Finally, the paper also deals with semantic segmentation, which is a natural language processing technique, and hence it could also belong to computational linguistics (cs.CL) category.
